{"tid":968092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國連鎖服裝店列 8 大中文告示！禁大媽在店內放屁？","createTime":"2019-01-04T03:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T06:00:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a54425f01d5ab310b4a227aea3ec4705b9fc60","tid":968092,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2240000/2242375/190103_shop_00_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2240000%2F2242375%2F190103_shop_00_1024.jpg&h=84deee59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要有人的地方，就會有中國旅客的存在，只不過不文明兼不尊重當地文化的旅客甚多，搞到有部分旅遊景點附近的地方，也要貼出中文告示作提醒。早前日本、韓國貼出告示的新聞屢見不鮮，而今次貼出中文告示的地方，就遠至德國！<br />\n<br />\n在 Facebook 群組中瘋傳的這張告示，其實是攝於德國連鎖服裝店舖 blutsgeschwister，當中更列出 8 大告示，當中首條就是「請不要在店內吃東西或者喝飲料」，還要放大字句，相信實在有太多大媽大叔在店內飲飲食食之故。<br />\n<br />\n其他禁止事項，包括：「本店不提供休息場所」、「請不要在店內剪手腳指甲」、「請不要在店內用牙簽剔牙」、「請不要在店內外隨地吐痰」、「我們謝絕講價，但是可以開購物退稅單」、「請不要過於大聲講話，以免影響其他顧客購物」。而最後一項就十分驚人，「請不要在店內打嗝或者放屁」，看來真的有大媽大叔做出此等行為，才有這個禁止事項。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2240000/2242375/190103_shop_01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2240000%2F2242375%2F190103_shop_01_600.jpg&h=d7f60a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2242375/德國連鎖服裝店列%208%20大中文告示！禁大媽在店內放屁？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2242375%2F%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%A3%E9%8E%96%E6%9C%8D%E8%A3%9D%E5%BA%97%E5%88%97%25208%2520%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%81%E7%A6%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%9C%A8%E5%BA%97%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BE%E5%B1%81%EF%BC%9F&d=pUPQkf61XcQGZPwxH5otP9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c1c5d532\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2242375/德國連鎖服裝店列%208%20大中文告示！禁大媽在店內放屁？</a>"},{"pid":"3a0517bcba5c91d8d1c729de7340c5652baca5bb","tid":968092,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"好委婉咁叫人唔好痾屎，有咩問題。"},{"pid":"6a818e9f5c4b0a2bb978ad93632f74758a4e10e5","tid":968092,"uid":182499,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"翻譯係香港人？ 用詞唔似贏國人風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95261a29a04dff548a786361bd81a23333fe4025","tid":968092,"uid":56467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"辱華 抵德 戰狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33c7e3b450dbc4534e4a1f6815a5eed73b58328","tid":968092,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:34:34.000Z","msg":"仲唔走去抵制？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21e8f397140a97ebad7596464d031ac2943e063","tid":968092,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"有埋英文喎"},{"pid":"c209f8857c659dd4ca5dc6359eac112aa6f866c1","tid":968092,"uid":48234,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b21e8f397140a97ebad7596464d031ac2943e063","tid":968092,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"有埋英文喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"邊撚度英文?德文嚟架"},{"pid":"3188c6ac90750820d470e73b9e6802e690dc0c18","tid":968092,"uid":16208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b21e8f397140a97ebad7596464d031ac2943e063","tid":968092,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"有埋英文喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"你肯定係英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /